import { Form, Button, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';

function AddCustomerModal() {
    return (
        <>
            <Form className='p-5' method='P'>


                <Row className="mb-3 p-1">
                    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formFirtsName">
                        <Form.Label>First name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type='text' name='formFirtsName' placeholder="First name" required />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Row>

                <Row className="mb-3 p-1">
                    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formLastName">
                        <Form.Label>Last name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type='text' name='formLastName' placeholder="Last name" required />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Row>

                <Row className="mb-3 p-1">
                    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formEmail">
                        <Form.Label>Email</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="email" name='formEmail' placeholder="Enter email" required />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Row>

                <Row className="mb-3 p-1">
                    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formPhone">
                        <Form.Label>Phone</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="phone" name='formPhone' placeholder="Enter Phone" />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Row>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3 p-1" controlId="formAddress1">
                    <Form.Label>Address</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='text' name='formAddress1' placeholder="1234 Main St" />
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group className="mb-3 p-1" controlId="formAddress2">
                    <Form.Label>Address 2</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='text' name='formAddress2' placeholder="Apartment, studio, or floor" />
                </Form.Group>

                <Row className="mb-3 p-1">
                    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formCity">
                        <Form.Label>City</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control name='formCity' />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Row>



                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                    Submit
                </Button>
            </Form>
        </>
    )
}

export default AddCustomerModal;
